    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Diagnosis unlikely to be made in the ED\nEvaluate for alternative diagnoses\nMRI Brain\n- usually increased T2 signal involving one or both temporal lobes.\n[1]\nLP\n- CSF w/lymphocytosis (though usually <100), elevated protein, normal glucose, elevated IgG index, oligoclonal bands\n[2]",
