        }
      ]
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "No randomized trials but may include\nIVIG\n,\nplasmapheresis\n,\ncorticosteroids\n,\ncyclophosphamide\nand/or\nrituximab\n.\n[3]\nTreat underlying malignancy",
